Detailed Description

cvmx_bgx::_spu::_an_lp_base

This register captures the contents of the latest AN link code word base page received from the link partner during autonegotiation. (See Std 802.3 section 73.6 for details.) BGX()_SPU()_AN_STATUS[PAGE_RX] is set when this register is updated by hardware.
